-- Demand for Polish PKO BP's euro bond tops 1.5 bln euros - IFR
-- 
-- Thu Jan 16, 2014 05:22AM EST
-- None



WARSAW, Jan 16 (Reuters) - Investors' demand for the 5-year euro bond of Poland's largest bank PKO BP <PKO.WA> has exceeded 1.5 billion euros, with the price guidance set at 125 basis points above mid-swaps, Thomson Reuters news and analysis service IFR said on Thursday.

